sequenceDiagram
    participant Camera as IP Camera
    participant Worker as Local Worker Server
    participant R2 as Cloudflare R2
    participant Processor as Hostinger VPS Python App
    participant Supabase as Supabase

    Camera->>Worker: Envía video feed
    Worker->>Worker: Procesa y cifra video localmente
    Worker->>R2: Almacena video cifrado

    loop Polling de videos pendientes
        Processor->>R2: Consulta videos pendientes de procesar
        R2-->>Processor: Retorna video pendiente
        Processor->>Processor: Analiza video y cuenta ovejas
        Processor->>R2: Almacena video procesado
        Processor->>Supabase: Guarda resultado de inteligencia y conteo
        Supabase-->>Processor: Confirma persistencia
    end